extendedInfo.description: NOTE: IF YOU HAVE ANY ISSUES WITH THIS APP, PLEASE LET US KNOW: SUPPORT@BYTEFOX.COM"My Autumn Tree HD" is a lovely designed free of charge live wallpaper for your smartphone or tablet device. It is absolutely free of ads and requires no special permissions. It includes a hand-drawn tree with an interactive swing and other nice animations.FREE version:- Free of ads- No permissions required- HD graphics- Very smooth parallax scrolling (swipe) (e.g. 60fps on Galaxy S2)- Touchable, animated swing- Cool effects (e.g. lens flare)- 10+ beautiful parallax layersPRO version:- Four Seasons (Spring, Summer, Autumn and Winter)- Day and Night for every season (with sparkling stars and fireflies) Theme- Many custom settings possible (heart initials, butterfly colors etc.)- Auto change Day & Night themeNote:Please try our free version first, to ensure that our App goes well on your device.Thank you very much!
